formattedAddress: 1490 E Buena Vista Dr (Walt Disney World)

items.summary: Lots of people like this place

pageInfo.description: Follow Walt Disney World Resort on Foursquare and be sure to check-in during your visit to unlock a little extra magic.

items.text: Downtown Disney offers a wide variety of shops and restaurants. You might also catch some live music and all for free! They also offer a hot air ballon ride as well. (Check prices)
Bowling alley called "Splittsville" has indoor/outdoor dining spots. The cheese pizza was really good.

Ghirardelli has free chocolate samples. The new Town Center area that just opened up this week is so fancy and beautiful. There is way more parking, more stores. More rest areas and bathrooms. Amazed.
Everything
There's a lot of walking involved from the parking to the shopping areas.  Be prepared for stressful parking if you try the parking garage.  It's worth it for all the shops and restaurants though
Wow! So much to do here! Restaurants, shopping, shows! Great place for a 2 hour evening!
OMG! If you happen to have some spare hours, you should DEFINITELY go to the AMC Dine-In Theater!! Servers come during the movie and bring your food right ro your reclining chair!
Nice place to have fun with family, kids really enjoyed the atmosphere. Have everything from shops, restaurants, movie theatre and bowling alley
Open late. Great shops and boutiques you can't find easily anywhere else. Bring your wallet. You're gonna need it.
Ghirardelli ice cream is outstanding! Order some and then sit by the lake and watch the volcano erupt for a relaxing time.
All kinds of shops. Check out the Lego store, the Disney store and Ghiradelli in particular.
Almost Everything
Always a fun time to shop and explore. Must see shopping includes: World of Disney, Fun Finds, The Lego Store, Pin Traders and Days of Christmas.
Free walking
Awesome...!
Walk through the entire area and take Water taxi on the way back. Good food, gaming & shopping options available.
Lots of construction going on. New shops and restaurants are already coming up. Great for a stroll in the evening. Some unique shops and restaurants.
T-Rex  Restaurant, restaurante temático de comida típica americana, con muy buen ambiente y excelente atención. Muy buena opción para familias con niños
Bongos Cuban cafe.
Está muito diferente! Tem muita coisa construindo é muito mais opções de restaurantes ! O que achei excelente foi o prédio para estacionamento grátis !!
